  "instructions": [
    "In a bowl, combine beef strips with salt, pepper, minced garlic, soy sauce, calamansi juice, and white wine; let marinate for 20 minutes.",
    "Dredge marinated beef in flour, dip in beaten eggs, then coat with bread crumbs, shaking off excess.",
    "In a skillet, heat vegetable oil over medium-high; add a tablespoon of butter for flavor.",
    "Fry the breaded beef strips until golden brown on each side, about 3 minutes per side, then remove to a plate.",
    "In the same skillet, sauté sliced onions in the remaining oil until translucent, about 4 minutes.",
    "Return the beef to the skillet, toss with onions, and cook for an additional 2 minutes to meld flavors.",
    "Plate the beef with onions, drizzle any leftover pan juices, and serve hot."
  ],
